duck: Transcendence (religion), the concept of being entirely beyond the universe (Not a living being). - In religion, transcendence refers to the aspect of God's nature and power which is wholly independent of (and removed from) the material universe.
Transcendence (philosophy), climbing or going beyond some philosophical concept or limit
Transcendence, transcendent, and transcendental are words that refer to an object (or a property of an object) as being comparatively beyond that of other objects.
transcendence definition: the quality or state of being transcendent.

milestones: 1960's guru icon Maharishi Mahesh Yogi dies

wiki.text:
'Transcendence', 'transcendent', and 'transcendental' are words that refer to
an object (or a property of an object) as being comparatively beyond that of
other objects. Such objects (or properties) transcend other objects (or
properties) in some way.
